#### 7. For each customer, how many delivered pizzas had at least 1 change and how many? and no changes?


::: {.cell}

```{.sql .cell-code}
-- PART 1
-- delivered orders
with cte1 as (
    select *
    from runner_orders
    where cancellation is null
        or cancellation in ('null', '')
),
-- orders with at least 1 changes
cte2 as (
    select *
    from customer_orders
    where exclusions <> ''
        and extras <> ''
        or (
